name: Leprino Foods WHEY PROTEIN CONCENTRATE FOR NUTRITION BARS (WPC NB)
description: Leprino Foods Whey Protein Concentrate for Nutrition Bars (WPC NB) was specifically developed to improve the quality of protein nutritional bars. Using WPC NB 80% improves the moistness and texture, and extends the shelf life of your bar. WPC 80% NB is made only from ultra-filtered mozzarella whey to ensure the highest nutritional protein quality. Entire production is OU Kosher and EU approved.
